# Trivy Ignore File
# This file is used to ignore known vulnerabilities that are:
# - False positives
# - Acceptable risks in the context
# - Already mitigated
# 
# Format:
# AVD-XXXX (or CVE-XXXX)
# 
# Example:
# AVD-AZU-0001
# CVE-2021-12345

# Add vulnerabilities to ignore below
# Make sure to document WHY each vulnerability is being ignored

# Example entries (uncomment if needed):
# CVE-2023-12345  # False positive in unused dependency
# AVD-AWS-0001    # AWS-specific issue mitigated by configuration
